      main = "Bivariate plots with histograms and smooth curves")

pairs(div2[ , 16:32], lower.panel = panel.smooth, upper.panel = panel.cor, 
      method = "pearson", diag.panel = panel.hist, 
      main = "Bivariate plots with histograms and smooth curves")
